IBOU TALKED ABOUT YOU
IN HIS LETTERS.

914
01:14:50,301 --> 01:14:53,500
YOU KNOW WHAT 
HE CALLED YOU?

915
01:14:53,500 --> 01:14:55,567
"THE GOOD MAN."

916
01:14:55,567 --> 01:14:58,401
 <i>HE ANSWERS AD</i>
 <i>TO SHARE RENT</i>

917
01:14:58,401 --> 01:15:00,667
 <i>AND YOU TREAT HIM</i>
 <i>LIKE A FRIEND.</i>

918
01:15:00,667 --> 01:15:04,734
