ABOUT YOU A LOT.

919
01:15:04,734 --> 01:15:07,167
YOU ARE A GOOD MAN.

920
01:15:07,167 --> 01:15:10,067
YOU GAVE HIM HEART.

921
01:15:10,067 --> 01:15:12,267
YOU GAVE HIM MAGIC.

922
01:15:16,434 --> 01:15:20,101
THAT IS HOW I WILL--
I WILL THINK OF YOU.

923
