I DON'T WANT YOU
TO THINK OF ME. 

924
01:15:24,334 --> 01:15:27,301
I DON'T WANT IT TO BE
IN THE PAST TENSE.

925
01:15:29,667 --> 01:15:32,034
I MADE A MISTAKE.

926
01:15:32,034 --> 01:15:36,201
WHAT DO YOU WANT?
ME TO COME TO AMERICA
WITH YOU?

927
01:15:36,201 --> 01:15:39,368
GET MY GREEN CARD?

928
01:15:39,368 --> 01:15:43,301
DO YOU-- YOU WANT
TO STAY HERE

929
01:15:43,301 --> 01:15:45,234
IN DAKAR WITH ME?

930
01:15:49,500 --> 01:15:52,834
WHAT-- WHAT HAPPENED
WITH US WAS...

931
01:15:52,834 --> 01:15:55,567
A FANTASY.

932
01:15:55,567 --> 01:15:57,800
THIS IS
WHERE I LIVE.

933
01:15:57,800 --> 01:16:00,767
 <i>MY FRIENDS</i>
 <i>ARE HERE.</i>

934
01:16:02,401 --> 01:16:06,567
IT HAS ITS OWN SMELLS,
THIS COUNTRY.

935
01:16:06,567 --> 01:16:08,500
I MISSED IT.

936
01:16:09,667 --> 01:16:12,067
I LIKE IT HERE.

937
01:16:13,800 --> 01:16:16,067
THIS IS MY HOME.

938
01:16:18,368 --> 01:16:20,734
( speaks Wolof )

939
01:16:22,401 --> 01:16:25,301
EXCUSE ME.

940
01:17:08,267 --> 01:17:11,667
 <i>( thunder rumbling )</i>

941
