NO NO,
IT'S NO PROBLEM AT ALL.

942
01:20:13,134 --> 01:20:14,900
( indistinct speaking )

943
01:20:38,301 --> 01:20:41,001
SO HOW ARE THINGS?

944
01:20:41,001 --> 01:20:43,500
I MEAN, AT SCHOOL
AND STUFF.

945
01:20:45,067 --> 01:20:47,034
THEY'RE OKAY.

946
01:20:50,633 --> 01:20:53,001
SOME OF THE KIDS...

947
01:20:53,001 --> 01:20:55,368
MAKE FUN OF ME
SOMETIMES.

948
01:20:57,967 --> 01:21:01,101
WELL, THE WORLD CAN BE
A BAD PLACE.

949
01:21:01,101 --> 01:21:04,167
SOMETIMES PEOPLE ACT
LIKE ASSHOLES

950
01:21:04,167 --> 01:21:06,368
JUST TO FIT IN.

951
