BUT MOST PEOPLE
ARE BASICALLY OKAY.

955
01:21:17,967 --> 01:21:21,134
WHAT ABOUT THE MAN?

956
01:21:21,134 --> 01:21:23,533
HE'S A SCHMUCK,

957
