YOU'RE MY DAD.

966
01:21:53,067 --> 01:21:56,134
WELL, I WOULD TELL YOU
IF YOU WERE A DEPRESSING,
UGLY LITTLE SHIT.

967
01:21:56,134 --> 01:21:58,267
NO, YOU WOULDN'T.

968
01:22:01,767 --> 01:22:03,700
BYE, DAD.

969
01:22:03,700 --> 01:22:05,533
BYE.

970
01:22:40,434 --> 01:22:42,633
( inaudible )

971
